data.description: Newly Renovated 2 Unit Multifamily Building in Washington Heights! Recently Appraised OVER the asking price!! This beautiful brick building will CASH FLOW on day one making for a perfect investment. Both units are 2 Beds / 1 Bath with a spacious and separate living room & dining room, open concept kitchen with a large pantry, new laminate flooring throughout (2021), updated bathrooms (2021), renovated kitchens w/ backsplash (2021), freshly painted (2021) and much more! The porch was rebuilt to code (2021), a new concrete sidewalk in the front (2021) and the roof has been inspected and is in good condition with plenty of life remaining. The fenced-in backyard is a perfect spot for summertime activities and grilling. Additional revenue stream opportunities with the full unfinished basement which can be duplexed or an in-law suite, install coin laundry and rent out parking spaces in the 2-car garage. FHA loan possibilities make for a great owner-occupied investment. Don't miss your opportunity! Check out the 3D virtual tour and call today to schedule your showing.
